---
import { Image } from "@astrojs/image/components";
import examsheets from "../../assets/images/examsheets.png";
import laptop from "../../assets/images/laptop.png";
import puzzle from "../../assets/images/puzzle.png";
---

<div class="bg-accent py-8 px-10">
  <h1 class="pb-3 text-left text-4xl text-secondary md:text-center md:text-2xl">
    What we do
  </h1>
  <p class="text-left text-2xl md:text-center md:text-xl">
    We are partners on your digital journey, furthering your core mission and
    impact. We lend our software engineering expertise strategically to
    accelerate and support the work you are already doing to benefit our
    society.
  </p>
  <div
    class="mt-28 flex flex-col justify-center gap-32 px-8 md:flex-row md:justify-between md:gap-5 md:px-0"
  >
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center bg-base-100 drop-shadow-xl">
      <Image class="-mt-24 mb-4 w-2/3" src={examsheets} alt="examsheets" />
      <div class="items-left flex flex-col px-10 pb-6">
        <h3 class="text-2xl text-secondary md:text-xl">Identify gaps</h3>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-base">
          We interview your key stakeholders to examine the limits of your
          current tools - and how those limits may weaken your mission.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center bg-base-100 drop-shadow-xl">
      <Image class="-mt-16 mb-8 w-2/3 md:mb-9" src={laptop} alt="laptop" />
      <div class="items-left flex flex-col px-10 pb-6">
        <h3 class="text-2xl text-secondary md:text-xl">Strategize</h3>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-base">
          We determine where our expertise should be exercised, then develop and
          share a comprehensive plan to capture the most impactful
          opportunities.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center bg-base-100 drop-shadow-xl">
      <Image class="-mt-24 mb-4 w-2/3" src={puzzle} alt="puzzle" />
      <div class="items-left flex flex-col px-10 pb-6">
        <h3 class="text-2xl text-secondary md:text-xl">Build</h3>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-base">
          We build the software that bridges any identified gaps and work with
          your team to develop expertise in your new custom built tools.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
